Maxwell Morton , 16, has been charged with first-degree murder in the death of Ryan Mangan , 16 . 
  Mangan was found dead at his home February 4 with a gunshot wound to the face . 
  Morton was identified after he sent a selfie of himself posing with his body to a friend on Snapchat . 
  His lawyer says the shooting was an accident and that Morton and Mangan were friends . 
  He was ordered to stand trial for murder and possession of a firearm . 
 